name: THE NINE-HEADED DRAGON IS YOU
description:
An infinitely variant portrait artwork based on the legend of the Nine-Headed Dragon of Hakone from Japanese mythology - Kuzuryū Daimyōjin. The artwork produced reflects your true self, based on your wallet address. Which dragon head are you? Fire a white-feathered arrow and see...

Artwork seeds by Wily Guys, code by Liam Egan.
